}}</ref> He is the founder of the '''Steve Aoki Charitable Fund,''' which raises money for global humanitarian relief organizations and medical research. Among the organization's fundraising methods are Aoki's touring events, "memorabilia auctions", and collaborations with other artists.<ref name="Rokellercharitable">
